dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Juan Rivera. May I please have your name?
Hi, my name is Amy Bell.
Nice to meet you, Amy. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Of course, my policy number is five six seven eight nine.
Thank you, Amy. Can you also confirm the make and model of the vehicle involved in the incident?
The vehicle is a two zero zero eight Honda Civic.
Great, thank you for the information, Amy. Is there a phone number I can reach you at for further updates?
Yes, you can reach me at seven one four two zero zero eight.
Thank you for providing the details, Amy. We will look into your claim and follow up with you soon. If you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
Thank you for your time, Amy. Have a great day!
Thank you, Juan. You too! Goodbye.
